    </p>
  </h2>
  <h2 data-sourcepos="38:1-38:14" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">第一章：SSL证书简介</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h2>
  <h3 data-sourcepos="40:1-40:17" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.1 什么是SSL证书？</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h3>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="42:1-42:19" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.1.1 SSL 证书的定义</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="44:1-44:83" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">SSL证书（Secure Sockets Layer Certificate），中文又译为安全套接层证书，是数字证书的一种，用于建立客户端和服务器之间安全的网络连接。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="46:1-46:37" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">SSL证书可以用于验证服务器的身份，并加密通信内容，防止数据被窃取或篡改。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="48:1-48:35" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">在互联网上，SSL证书被广泛评估各种网站、电子商务、在线支付等场景。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
  </h2>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="50:1-50:19" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.1.2 SSL证书的作用</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="52:1-52:20" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">SSL证书的作用主要体现在以下几个方面：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <ul data-sourcepos="54:1-57:0" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 4px 0px; padding-inline-start: 1.125rem;">
      <li data-sourcepos="54:1-54:43" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">保护用户隐私：SSL证书可以加密通信内容，防止数据被窃取或篡改，保护用户隐私安全。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="55:1-55:43" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">维护网站安全：SSL证书可以验证服务器的身份，防止假冒网站欺骗用户，维护网站安全。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="56:1-57:0" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">提升网站信任度：使用SSL证书的网站，会在浏览器地址栏显示绿色安全锁图标，提升用户对网站的信任度。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </h2>
  <h3 data-sourcepos="58:1-58:20" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">1.2为什么SSL证书很重要？</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h3>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="60:1-60:21" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">SSL证书之所以重要，主要有以下几个原因：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <ul data-sourcepos="62:1-65:0" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 4px 0px; padding-inline-start: 1.125rem;">
      <li data-sourcepos="62:1-62:102" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**保护用户隐私：**在互联网上，用户经常会输入个人信息、银行卡信息等敏感数据，这些数据如果没有得到有效的保护，很容易被窃取或泄露。SSL证书可以加密通信内容，防止数据被窃取或篡改，保护用户隐私安全。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="63:1-63:110" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**维护网站安全：**随着互联网技术的不断发展，网络攻击手段也越来越丰富。一些不法分子可能会创建假冒网站，欺骗用户输入个人信息或进行其他恶意操作。SSL证书验证服务器的身份，防止假冒网站欺骗用户，维护网站安全。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="64:1-65:0" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**提升网站信任度：**在浏览器地址栏绿色安全锁图标是SSL证书的重要标志之一。当用户看到这个图标时，就会该网站是安全的，从而提高对网站的信任度信任度。这对于网站来说至关重要，因为用户只有在信任网站的情况下才会放心进行交易。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </h2>
  <h2 data-sourcepos="66:1-66:14" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">第二章：获取SSL证书</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h2>
  <h3 data-sourcepos="68:1-68:19" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.1 SSL证书获取方式概述</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h3>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="70:1-70:22" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">获取SSL证书的方式有多种，常见的方式包括：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <ul data-sourcepos="72:1-75:0" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 4px 0px; padding-inline-start: 1.125rem;">
      <li data-sourcepos="72:1-72:45" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**免费的SSL证书：**一些机构提供免费的SSL证书，例如Let's Encrypt。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="73:1-73:47" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**付费SSL证书：**一些机构提供付费SSL证书，例如GoDaddy、Comodo等。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
      <li data-sourcepos="74:1-75:0" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">**自签名SSL证书：**用户也可以自己签名SSL证书，但这种证书通常不被浏览器信任。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p data-sourcepos="76:1-76:38" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">下面，我们以 Let's Encrypt 为例，介绍一下如何获取免费的 SSL 证书。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
  </h2>
  <h3 data-sourcepos="78:1-78:36" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.2 从Let's Encrypt获取免费SSL证书的详细步骤</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h3>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="80:1-80:20" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.2.1 前提条件：域名准备</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="82:1-82:23" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">首先，您需要准备一个域名，用于申请SSL证书。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="84:1-84:25" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">如果您还没有域名，可以前往域名注册商注册一个域名。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
  </h2>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="86:1-86:23" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.2.2步骤1：安装Acme脚本</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="88:1-88:25" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Acme 脚本是一个用于申请和管理 SSL 证书的工具。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
