  </h2>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="3:1-3:19" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.2.3步骤2：申请证书</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:27" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">安装Acme脚本后，您可以使用以下命令申请SSL证书：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block ng-star-inserted" style="border-radius: 12px; margin: 16px 0px; position: relative;">
      <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block-internal-container" style="border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px;">
        <pre _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"><code _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-container no-decoration-radius" data-sourcepos="7:1-9:54" data-test-id="code-content" role="text" style="border-radius: 12px; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-feature-settings: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size: 0.875rem; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.125rem; overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px 16px 22px;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc;">~/.acme.sh/acme.sh --issue -d example.com --standalone
</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p data-sourcepos="11:1-11:22" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="background-color: #cccccc;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">其中，</span></span></span></span></span></span><code style="border-radius: 6px; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.25rem; padding: 1px 6px;">example.com</code><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">是您的域名。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="13:1-13:23" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">如果您的域名需要通符配支持，可以使用以下命令：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block ng-star-inserted" style="border-radius: 12px; margin: 16px 0px; position: relative;">
      <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block-internal-container" style="border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px;">
        <pre _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"><code _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-container no-decoration-radius" data-sourcepos="15:1-17:58" data-test-id="code-content" role="text" style="border-radius: 12px; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-feature-settings: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size: 0.875rem; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.125rem; overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px 16px 22px;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc;">~/.acme.sh/acme.sh --issue -d "*.example.com" --standalone
</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </h2>
  <h4 data-sourcepos="19:1-19:19" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">2.2.4步骤3：安装证书</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h4>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="21:1-21:23" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">申请成功后，您可以使用以下命令安装SSL证书：</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block ng-star-inserted" style="border-radius: 12px; margin: 16px 0px; position: relative;">
      <div _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-block-internal-container" style="border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px;">
        <pre _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"><code _ngcontent-ng-c987575795="" class="code-container no-decoration-radius" data-sourcepos="23:1-25:141" data-test-id="code-content" role="text" style="border-radius: 12px; direction: ltr; display: block; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-feature-settings: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size: 0.875rem; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.125rem; overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px 16px 22px;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc;">~/.acme.sh/acme.sh --installcert -d example.com --key-file /etc/letsencrypt/example.com.key --fullchain-file /etc/letsencrypt/example.com.crt
</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p data-sourcepos="27:1-27:87" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="background-color: #cccccc;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">其中，</span></span></span></span></span></span><code style="border-radius: 6px; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.25rem; padding: 1px 6px;">/etc/letsencrypt/example.com.key</code><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">是您的私钥文件，</span></span></span></span></span></span><code style="border-radius: 6px; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.25rem; padding: 1px 6px;">/etc/letsencrypt/example.com.crt</code><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">是您的证书文件。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="29:1-29:28" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">安装证书后，您的网站就可以使用SSL证书进行安全连接了。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
  </h2>
  <h2 data-sourcepos="31:1-31:11" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin: 2.75rem 0px 1rem;">
    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">第三章：其他资源</span></span></span></span></span></span>
