    <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">后记</span></span></span></span></span></span>
  </h2>
  <h2>
    <p data-sourcepos="41:1-41:50" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">以上内容介绍了SSL证书的基础知识以及如何从Let's Encrypt获取免费SSL证书的详细步骤。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="43:1-43:59" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">需要注意的是，SSL 证书的有效期通常为一年，需要定期更新。您可以使用 Acme 脚本提供的自动更新功能来简化证书续订流程。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="45:1-45:29" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: #cccccc; vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">希望本内容对您有所帮助。如果您还有其他问题，可以留言交流。</span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <p data-sourcepos="47:1-47:8" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 1rem 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; word-break: break-word;">
      <span style="background-color: #cccccc; font-weight: 700;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">请注意：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
    </p>
    <ul data-sourcepos="49:1-52:0" style="font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 4px 0px; padding-inline-start: 1.125rem;">
      <li data-sourcepos="49:1-49:19" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
